data.description: Nestled in the heart of Parker, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquil living and serene outdoor spaces. The greenery, mature trees and level pastures offer a functional space for all of your animals or outdoor toys. This home presents a canvas of possibilities for a buyer to come in and put their personal touches on. All of the major mechanicals have been updated in the recent years, including newer furnace, A/C, carpet and tile. The main living areas are bathed in natural light and the open-concept layout effortlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, ensuring a seamless flow for both daily routines and entertaining. Upstairs, there are 3 well-appointed bedrooms, including the primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom and an additional full bathroom. The basement is fully finished with laundry and the potential to create a fourth bedroom. The generous yard offers endless possibilities to create your very own retreat. Bring your horses home to enjoy this four-stall barn with a tack room, wash stall and feed storage. The barn has runs off of each stall and adjacent to the barn are two additional shed rows. There are multiple flat pastures to use as you wish. This home is an escape from civilization with everyday conveniences at your fingertips, situated within easy reach of major highways, schools, shopping centers, and recreational areas, but with plenty of privacy. Immerse yourself in the beauty of Parker's scenic landscapes, with parks, trails, and open spaces, perfect for those seeking an active lifestyle. Seize the opportunity to make this exceptional residence your own!
